    <section id="configuration">
        <h3>Configuration
            <small>methods
            <a class="headerlink" href="#configuration" title="Permalink to this headline">¶</a></small>
        </h3>

        <ul>
            <li>IpBlackList <strong>blockAddress</strong> (string $address) - Specify an address to be blocked.
                This can be an IP4, IP6, or named address
            </li>
            <li>IpBlackList <strong>unblockAddress</strong> (string $address) - Unblock and address that was
                previously blocked
            </li>
            <li>boolean <strong>isBlocked</strong> (string $address) - Check to see if an address is being
                blocked
            </li>
            <li>array <strong>getBlockedAddresses</strong> () - Return an indexed array of all the addresses
